      "updated": 1772434948
    },
    {
      "id": "69a535a2000000000092c2d3",
      "text": "Drawingで書いた画像は白地に黒文字になり、ページ背景から浮く",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772434850,
      "updated": 1772435856
    },
    {
      "id": "69a53951000000000092c2fc",
      "text": " Drawingの背景は透過でなく白なので",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772435793,
      "updated": 1772435860
    },
    {
      "id": "69a535a2000000000092c2d4",
      "text": " [このページだけ昼]というリンクが付いているページでダークテーマを解除する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772434850,
      "updated": 1772435772
    },
    {
      "id": "69a535a2000000000092c2d5",
      "text": "  CSSで`page:has(href=\"/villagepump/このページだけ昼)`で解除できるはずだが大変そう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772434850,
      "updated": 1772435910
    },
    {
      "id": "69a539ce000000000092c303",
      "text": " 解決策",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772435919,
      "updated": 1772435927
    },
    {
      "id": "69a539d5000000000092c305",
      "text": "  ブラウザをライトモードにして見る",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772435925,
      "updated": 1772435925
    },
    {
      "id": "69a539d0000000000092c304",
      "text": "  [/scrapboxlab]にページを移動する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1772435920,
      "updated": 1772435937
    },
    {
      "id": "69a54c6500000000009eefaa",
      "text": "そのうち手書き文字をフォント化しだす[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772440677,
      "updated": 1772440692
    },
    {
      "id": "69a54c7b00000000009eefac",
      "text": "\t車輪の再発明（活版印刷の再発明）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1772440699,
      "updated": 1772440727
    },
